From e4b6291a0f7e8ac1e7a9f5148ef66973820a95fb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thirusenthil Kumaran J <thirusen@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Jun 2025 20:15:43 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 04/10] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL: hostapd: Clean up and refactor 6 GHz
 EIRP APIs

Move the definitions for the APIs used for querying the EIRP power
from the file 'ieee802_11.c' to 'hostapd.c' for usage in other files

Add an API to get the corresponding 6 GHz channel data structure
for a given frequency from hostapd modes structure. Use this API
to get the regulatory EIRP for the 6 GHz channel.

Fixes: None
Patch-work: None
Tag: 6G_REGULATORY
Feature: AFC
Patch-dependency:
n00-001-hostapd-add-support-for-6GHz-operation.patch
r32-001-hostapd-Add-support-to-receive-AFC-power-update-comp.patch
r72-a-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-hostapd-6-GHz-power-mode-channels-.patch

Signed-off-by: Thirusenthil Kumaran J <thirusen@qti.qualcomm.com>
